{"text": "I paid $12 for this game. I've currently played 250 hours... which is too much, but I always come back. $12 / 250hr = $0.05/hr Best value ever. The game is so cheap but such replayability. I'd recommend it for anyone into immersive FPS games that aren't all about run and gun. And because it's all about getting the drop on the opponent, you don't have to be a dorito-eating mountain dew-drinking basement twitch shooter to enjoy it. Great fun!!", "appid": "222880", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042162605", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1451044800.0}
